§ 4. References (design inspiration, no source code copied)
-----------------------------------------------------------

The following project was studied while designing K-Balabolka's macttssink
plugin. No source code was copied from it; K-Balabolka's plugin is written
from scratch in C / Objective-C. This section is provided for academic
honesty and traceability, not to discharge any license obligation.

- avstack/gst-ttssink
  Repository: https://github.com/avstack/gst-ttssink
  License:    MIT OR Apache-2.0 (dual-licensed, per its Cargo.toml)
  Note:       A Rust-based, cross-platform GStreamer TTS sink. K-Balabolka
              was implemented independently in C / Objective-C against the
              same public GStreamer plugin API. The shared structure (a
              `GstBaseSink` subclass with `class_init` / `_init` / `render`)
              derives from GStreamer's own documented plugin pattern, not
              from this project.

The standard `GstBaseSink` subclassing boilerplate used throughout
`plugin/` is taken from the GStreamer plugin development documentation
and the GStreamer "good" plugin set, both LGPL-2.1-or-later.
